Strategically steered confidential patient pregnancy testing services, including objectively counseling and mentoring clients per individual needs, as well as accurately maintaining all client records and medical files. Optimized operations efficiency by performing key data entry, bookkeeping, and appointment scheduling.

Cultivated a high-quality business image with superior services by exceeding home healthcare standards, including completing errands and transporting clients to appointments, as well as performing housekeeping.

Played a vital role in performing routine housekeeping duties (e.g. washing dishes / clothes, making beds) for diverse clientele, including participating in frequent grocery shopping excursions per individual client needs.
